aima.core.logic.propositional.visitors

Class ConvertToCNF

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.logic.propositional.visitors.ConvertToCNF

  • public class ConvertToCNF
extends java.lang.Object
    Convert a Sentence into an equivalent Conjunctive Normal Form (CNF) Sentence. A Sentence is in CNF if it is a conjunction of disjunction of literals.
    Author:
    Ciaran O'Reilly
